</metadata>

<maincontent>

<!-- com.omniupdate.div label="maincontent" group="Everyone" button="707" --><!-- ouc:editor csspath="/_resources/ou/editor/maincontent.css" cssmenu="/_resources/ou/editor/classes.txt" width="1000"/ --><h3>How It Works</h3>
<p>Experiential learning is a required component of tCAP and gives students the opportunity to apply classroom knowledge in real-world environments.</p>
<table style="border-style: none;">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="border-style: none;">
<table class="media-small-left">
<thead>
