<strong><span style="color: #006747; font-size: 1.25em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase;">Choose an experience</span></strong>
<p>Select an eligible pathway such as an internship, research, capstone, hackathon or study abroad experience.</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>
<table class="media-small-left">
<thead>
<tr>
<th class="ou-help mceNonEditable">News - Image - Small - Left <br />Image Width: 100 px, Height: 100 px* <br />* Recommended Height.</th>
