<strong><span style="color: #006747; font-size: 1.25em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase;">Get pre-approval</span></strong>
<p>Pre-approval of a plan of work and faculty mentor or quality supervisor.</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>
<table class="media-small-left">
<thead>
<tr>
<th class="ou-help mceNonEditable">News - Image - Small - Left <br />Image Width: 100 px, Height: 100 px* <br />* Recommended Height.</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="image"><img src="{{f:82757025}}" alt="3" width="1254" height="1254" /></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<strong><span style="color: #006747; font-size: 1.25em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase;">Complete the work</span></strong>
<p>Meet the minimum threshold of 135 verified hours and deliver a mid-point update.</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>
