<strong><span style="color: #006747; font-size: 1.25em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase;">Reflect and record</span></strong>
<p>Develop and deliver a final report with structured reflection, pass/fail assessment and CIS 4950 notation.</p>
</td>
</tr>
