<h3>Approved Pathways</h3>
<p>Eligible experiences include internships, undergraduate research through USF Student Engagement in Research &amp; Innovation, capstone projects, cybersecurity support services, entrepreneurship initiatives, competitions, hackathons and study abroad experiences.</p>
<h3>Requirements</h3>
<table class="table-bordered" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"><caption>What Students Need to Complete</caption>
<thead>
<tr>
<th scope="col">Requirement</th>
<th scope="col">What it means</th>
<th scope="col">Student output<br />&nbsp;</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>135 verified hours</td>
<td>Minimum threshold of 135 verified hours</td>
<td>Tracked hours<br />&nbsp;</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Pre-approval</td>
<td>Pre-approval of a plan of work and faculty mentor or quality supervisor</td>
<td>Approved plan of work<br /><br /></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Documentation</td>
<td>Plan of work, mid-point update and final report with structured reflection</td>
<td>Plan, update and final report<br />&nbsp;</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Assessment</td>
<td>Pass/fail assessment using a common rubric</td>
<td>Pass/fail result</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>CIS 4950</td>
<td>Recorded as CIS 4950 (badge and transcript notation)</td>
<td>Badge and transcript notation<br /><br /></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table><!-- /com.omniupdate.div -->
